{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/68187", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/68187/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/68187/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/68187/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/68187", "id": 549147471, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU1NDkxNDc0NzE=", "number": 68187, "title": "tests unoptimized with opt-level = 2", "user": {"login": "giarc3", "id": 34786857, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjM0Nzg2ODU3", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/34786857?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3", "html_url": "https://github.com/giarc3", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2020-01-13T19:56:14Z", "updated_at": "2020-01-13T20:12:46Z", "closed_at": "2020-01-13T20:12:45Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "With a Cargo.toml that contains\r\n```\r\n[profile.dev]\r\nopt-level = 0\r\n\r\n[profile.test]\r\nopt-level = 2\r\n```\r\nrunning `cargo t --no-run --verbose` results in: \r\n```\r\nFinished test [unoptimized + debuginfo] target(s) in 2m 44s\r\n```\r\neven though `opt-level = 2` is included in the rustc command. This shows that the build did use the `test` profile, but did not add optimization.\r\n\r\n\r\nHowever, changing it to \r\n```\r\n[profile.dev]\r\nopt-level = 1\r\n\r\n[profile.test]\r\nopt-level = 2\r\n```\r\nand running `cargo t --no-run --verbose` results in: \r\n```\r\nFinished test [optimized + debuginfo] target(s) in 6m 39s\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis implies that test compilation uses optimization from `[profile.dev]` instead of `[profile.test]` as expected.\r\n\r\n## Meta\r\n`rustc --version --verbose`:\r\n```\r\nrustc 1.40.0 (73528e339 2019-12-16)\r\nbinary: rustc\r\ncommit-hash: 73528e339aae0f17a15ffa49a8ac608f50c6cf14\r\ncommit-date: 2019-12-16\r\nhost: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\r\nrelease: 1.40.0\r\nLLVM version: 9.0\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "giarc3", "id": 34786857, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjM0Nzg2ODU3", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/34786857?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3", "html_url": "https://github.com/giarc3", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/giarc3/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/68187/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "